thread.title: NFL Draft: Midround WRs that could interest Eagles after signing Alshon Jeffery, Torrey Smith
thread.title_full: NFL Draft: Midround WRs that could interest Eagles after signing Alshon Jeffery, Torrey Smith

author: Matt Lombardo | For NJ Advance Media
title: NFL Draft: Midround WRs that could interest Eagles after signing Alshon Jeffery, Torrey Smith
text: After signing Alshon Jeffery and Torrey Smith in free agency, the Eagles are unlikely to invest the No. 14 overall pick in the NFL Draft on another wide receiver but that doesn't mean Howie Roseman and Co. won't be aiming to further upgrade the talent at a position that has been one of the weakest on the roster in recent years.
